{"tid":1846734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想搞黎明既入一入黎","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T15:09:15.000Z","uid":23471,"like":26,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b34cf6f885b38d26dbb9ba52da6a360e92deec63","tid":1846734,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"首先我絶對支持三罷，但而加你地call手足去黨鐵 知唔知要手足take一個好危險既risk  好容易成為帶菌者or中肺炎 你話過去我地都為五大訴求咩未食過 但問題係我地今次唔係為過去7個月既手足爭取合理權益 唔係追究警暴濫權問題 而只係想政府封關之類 我哋係咪值得去咁做？ <br />\n<br />\n老實講你地話connect埋藍絲 我建議你地唔好咁多幻想 個班人自私自利 蛇齋餅糭就搶住要 其實肺炎係對老人相對較致命 對後生致命率較低(可能你地又話 後生中左又食steroid 會對骨點點) 但都好過即死 加上後生知識水平高 講求衛生程度高 中既機率一定較老人低 所以肺炎明顯對班廢老港豬影響大啲 何不由佢地做主導 唔出黎罷工咪佢地死先 <br />\n<br />\n你地都有留意到地鐵前幾日都有一個疑似中肺炎係車箱入面暈咗 班返工撚港豬咁中意咪自己take而啲risk 點解要我地手足冒而啲險 而且相對上肺炎對佢地影響較少 佢地班人過去又冇幫過我地 我地本身五大訴求都未得 點解要我地take而個risk幫佢地？ <br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得為左支持醫護罷工就夠 佢地中意返工就自己take而啲risk"},{"pid":"b09b8a48ac9dbf7658b93fa9ebef8dfd8cfc72ea","tid":1846734,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f6119ed04cbd32ffc9adc0fab09911d45c29dd0c","tid":1846734,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d1e01d32c95541f50946ca97006216a6a3bfe21","tid":1846734,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"美國獨立戰爭有大量freerider，係咪唔使打？"},{"pid":"6b27e85d987a02d3c1f9017b01000b9aea96fe4b","tid":1846734,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"岩阿<br />\n想死咪返工，返大公司既依家風險一定極高，目前評估傳染力最低好低都有成2.8，通風唔好就成層玩完。<br />\n<br />\nObjective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Los Angeles(NEW!), Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=208f013d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a><br />\nP牌無得推，得閒就入去推"},{"pid":"f2d89159195bfad1d426efc5f7332ce3bde9a839","tid":1846734,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"香港醫護唔罷工嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護自己在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edG0Z6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedG0Z6X.jpg&h=8ac5b79d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會支持醫護，一齊罷工保護香港，直至港府落實封關"},{"pid":"afeb6c98be5869fc332a13437e56259ced712cb3","tid":1846734,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"反而我覺得要針對大陸運動工具"},{"pid":"e6b6eef56bdd6099dd82bbd647aea642bf2ad69a","tid":1846734,"uid":23471,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d1e01d32c95541f50946ca97006216a6a3bfe21","tid":1846734,"uid":253978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:20:27.000